    "causal_summary": "Phase 003 of the numbered-prefix deprecation. Author one deterministic migration script that performs the whole de-numbering — git mv the 390 numbered category folders to bare slugs, rewrite the 115 frontmatter category: values, the ~1,052 root index-table path rows, the ~5,298 nav/cross-ref links across ~1,841 files, and the two SKILL.md router-prefix blocks — with a DRY-RUN mode that mutates nothing and emits a rename map, per-file diff, and safety/collision report. Honors the ADR-004 deny-list (z_archive, CHANGELOG, history, this packet's evidence). Tooling-only phase — Phase 004 runs it.",
